1d:["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-5","children":[["$","p","Our experienced and knowledgeable cost management expert understand the importance of delivering a project to meet your budget and financial expectations. We will work with clients to develop aspirations, offer best value for money and maximise budget efficiency.",{"className":"font-body text-base leading-8 text-brand-muted sm:text-lg","children":"Our experienced and knowledgeable cost management expert understand the importance of delivering a project to meet your budget and financial expectations. We will work with clients to develop aspirations, offer best value for money and maximise budget efficiency."}],["$","p","We provide expert advice on construction costs to ensure that proposed projects are affordable, commercially viable, and offer good value for money. We will help the client and the design team assess and compare different options, track variations, and ensuring that costs remain under control as the project progresses.",{"className":"font-body text-base leading-8 text-brand-muted sm:text-lg","children":"We provide expert advice on construction costs to ensure that proposed projects are affordable, commercially viable, and offer good value for money. We will help the client and the design team assess and compare different options, track variations, and ensuring that costs remain under control as the project progresses."}]]}]
1e:["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-5","children":[["$","p","Employers, Local Authorities and Housing Associations have the challenge of ensuring that their construction projects achieve value for money and are completed to a high quality in terms of workmanship, materials, construction standards and building regulation statutory compliance.",{"className":"font-body text-base leading-8 text-brand-muted sm:text-lg","children":"Employers, Local Authorities and Housing Associations have the challenge of ensuring that their construction projects achieve value for money and are completed to a high quality in terms of workmanship, materials, construction standards and building regulation statutory compliance."}],["$","p","As an independent third party, we will inspect projects to protect the Clients interests throughout the construction process. We will anticipate; interpret; inspect; record; report; advise and guide; help reduce risk; provide guidance on health and safety matters; assist in getting it right first time and issue comprehensive report for each site visit.",{"className":"font-body text-base leading-8 text-brand-muted sm:text-lg","children":"As an independent third party, we will inspect projects to protect the Clients interests throughout the construction process. We will anticipate; interpret; inspect; record; report; advise and guide; help reduce risk; provide guidance on health and safety matters; assist in getting it right first time and issue comprehensive report for each site visit."}]]}]
